            <title>[KAFKA-10223] ReplicaNotAvailableException must be retriable to handle reassignments</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-10223</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ReplicaNotAvailableException should be a retriable `InvalidMetadataException` since consumers may throw this during reassignments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
